# Hypercube GPU Core - NPM Exclusions
# Keep the package small and focused on the core simulation logic.

# Local Development & Housekeeping
node_modules/
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
*.log
perf_log.txt
benchmark_results/
walkthrough.md
.version_history.md
.agentrules
.agent_behavior.md

# Build Context
dist/
